<idea-plugin>
    <id>fr.jukien.intellij.plugins.pojo-generator</id>
    <name>POJO Generator</name>
    <vendor email="julien.diemer@efrei.net" url="https://github.com/Jukien">Julien DIEMER</vendor>

    <description><![CDATA[
    <h1>Generate JPA Entity POJO from database table</h1>
    <br/>
    Can generate from database table:<br/>
<ul>
    <li>
        an JPA Entity (JPA Annotated POJO)
        <ul>
            <li>There is no relationship between table</li>
            <li>JPA annotations are generates over attributes</li>
            <li>GeneratedValue annotations if sequence over column are auto generated (Tested with MySQL)</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>
        a Data Transfert Object
    </li>
</ul>
<br/>
For now, only works for some DataType with <b>MySQL</b>, <b>Oracle</b> & <b>PostgreSQL</b>.
<br/><br/>

Below the mapping table used by the plugin:<br/><br/>
<table>
    <thead>
    <tr>
        <th>DBMS</th>
        <th>SQL DataType</th>
        <th>Java DataType</th>
        <th>JPA columnDefinition</th>
    </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
    <tr>
        <td>MySQL</td>
        <td>bigint</td>
        <td>Long</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>MySQL</td>
        <td>bit</td>
        <td>Boolean</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>MySQL</td>
        <td>date</td>
        <td>java.sql.Date</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>MySQL</td>
        <td>datetime</td>
        <td>java.sql.Timestamp</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>MySQL</td>
        <td>double</td>
        <td>Double</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>MySQL</td>
        <td>int</td>
        <td>Integer</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>MySQL</td>
        <td>json</td>
        <td>String</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>MySQL</td>
        <td>varchar</td>
        <td>String</td>
    </tr>

    <tr>
        <td>Oracle</td>
        <td>CHAR</td>
        <td>String</td>
        <td>CHAR</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>Oracle</td>
        <td>DATE</td>
        <td>java.sql.Date</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>Oracle</td>
        <td>NUMBER</td>
        <td>Long</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>Oracle</td>
        <td>VARCHAR2</td>
        <td>String</td>
    </tr>

    <tr>
        <td>PostgreSQL</td>
        <td>bigint</td>
        <td>Long</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>PostgreSQL</td>
        <td>boolean</td>
        <td>Boolean</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>PostgreSQL</td>
        <td>date</td>
        <td>java.sql.Date</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>PostgreSQL</td>
        <td>integer</td>
        <td>Long</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>PostgreSQL</td>
        <td>varchar</td>
        <td>String</td>
    </tr>
    </tbody>
</table>
    ]]></description>

    <change-notes><![CDATA[
    <ul>
        <li>[Add] Possibility to customize the JPA mapping</li>
        <li>[Fixed] <a href="https://github.com/Jukien/POJO-Generator/issues/2">GitHub #2</a>(): Settings for New Projects were not saved</li>
    </ul>
    ]]></change-notes>

    <!-- please see http://www.jetbrains.org/intellij/sdk/docs/basics/getting_started/plugin_compatibility.html
         on how to target different products -->
    <!-- uncomment to enable plugin in all products
    <depends>com.intellij.modules.lang</depends>
    -->

    <depends>com.intellij.modules.java</depends>
    <depends>com.intellij.modules.ultimate</depends>
    <depends>com.intellij.modules.database</depends>

    <extensions defaultExtensionNs="com.intellij">
        <!-- Add your extensions here -->
        <projectConfigurable groupId="tools" displayName="POJO Generator" id="pojo-generator" instance="fr.jukien.intellij.plugins.ui.POJOGeneratorConfigurable">
            <configurable id="pojo-generator.jpa-mapping" displayName="JPA Mapping" instance="fr.jukien.intellij.plugins.ui.JPAMappingConfigurable"/>
        </projectConfigurable>
        <applicationService serviceImplementation="fr.jukien.intellij.plugins.ui.POJOGeneratorSettings"/>
        <applicationService serviceImplementation="fr.jukien.intellij.plugins.ui.JPAMappingSettings"/>
    </extensions>

    <actions>
        <!-- Add your actions here -->
        <group id="org.jetbrains.tutorials.actions.GroupedActions" text="POJO Generator" popup="true" icon="/META-INF/pluginIcon.svg">
            <add-to-group group-id="DatabaseViewPopupMenu" anchor="after" relative-to-action="DatabaseView.RunExtensionScriptGroup"/>
            <action id="entity" class="fr.jukien.intellij.plugins.action.Entity" text="Entity" description="Generate an Entity" icon="/META-INF/pluginIcon.svg"/>
            <action id="dto" class="fr.jukien.intellij.plugins.action.DTO" text="DTO" description="Generate a Data Transfert Object" icon="/META-INF/pluginIcon.svg"/>
        </group>
    </actions>
</idea-plugin>
